  "text": "Expression of SDF-1 was determined on isolated platelets and HAECs with 1-color flow cytometry as described previously. [CITATION_1] CD34 \u03e9 cells, HAECs, and progenitor cell-derived endothelial cells were tested for expression of CD146, ICAM-1 (intercellular adhesion molecule-1), VE-cadherin (vascular endothelial cadherin), PECAM-1 (platelet/endothelial cell adhesion molecule-1), CD34, CD18, and CD45.",
